, 
<figureCitation id="13292A67FFA6FF83E19B2387BB72FDEB" box="[243,271,511,535]" captionStart="FIGURE 11" captionStartId="25.[151,250,1869,1891]" captionTargetBox="[184,1395,202,1838]" captionTargetId="figure@25.[174,1410,193,1842]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="FIGURE 11. Genitalia. a, male actorion, Guyana (dissection Penz 12 - 01, CMNH); b, female actorion, Guyana (dissection Penz 10 - 02, LACM; scale bar different from male illustrations); c, male decaerulea, Lectotype, Brazil, Pará, Faro, (dissection Miller 9047, MfN); d, male rebeli, Peru, San Martín (dissection Penz 10 - 08, USNM); e, male caelestis, paratype, Brazil, Amazonas, São Paulo de Olivença (dissection Penz 10 - 29, CMNH); f, male pucallpa, Peru, Pucallpa (USUSNM 2041410); g, male peruana, Peru, Huanuco, Rio Pichis (dissection Penz 09 - 06, FLMNH)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/569741/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="211">11</figureCitation>
